    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1908-09-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1908-09-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="346"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d346">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 6775/578.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of Guatemala</gloss> to
                        President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-09-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 16, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have the honor and great satisfaction to inform you that under the pleasantest
                    auspices the International Central American Bureau has been inaugurated. By
                    reason of this, kindly accept my patriotic gratitude and warm greetings in the
                    name of Guatemala and in my own.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">M. Estrada C.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
